Beef and mushroom bolognese is a hearty and flavourful pasta sauce made with ground beef, mushrooms, and a variety of vegetables simmered in a rich tomato sauce. It’s a delicious and satisfying meal that is perfect for a cozy night in or for entertaining friends and family. Whether you’re a seasoned cook or a beginner in the kitchen, this recipe by the South African Mushroom Farmer’s Association is sure to become a family favourite. 